[BACKGROUND]
Color:      Off-white, warm — slightly creamy #f0ece4 tone
Texture:    Flat wall surface — matte, no texture detail
Gradient:   None — even, uniform coverage

[LIGHTING]
Type:       Hard directional flash or tungsten — single source
Direction:  Front-facing, slightly right of camera axis
Intensity:  High — overexposed whites, flat bright coverage on background
Falloff:    Minimal — light hits background directly, very little shadow rolloff

[SHADOWS]
Type:       Hard-edged cast shadow on background wall
Direction:  Shadow falls directly behind and slightly left — strong, graphic
Opacity:    Deep, defined — high contrast against bright wall
Style:      Shadow is a feature, not an accident — editorial, intentional
Offset:     Shadow visibly separated from object — not contact shadow

[FILM QUALITY]
Grain:      Visible film grain — analog feel, 35mm aesthetic
Tone:       Slightly warm, slightly faded — not clinical, lived-in
Saturation: Low-medium — muted, not vibrant

[MOOD]
Style:      Candid editorial — indie magazine, analog photography
Reference:  35mm film portrait lighting applied to product
